    "body": "This PR introduces minor changes to improve the messages prompted to users when the DB is empty.\r\n\r\nCurrent messages:\r\n```console\r\n$ spack find\r\n==> No package matches the query: []\r\n\r\n$ spack uninstall -a\r\n==> Error: <built-in function any> does not match any installed packages.\r\n==> Error: You can either:\r\n    a) Use a more specific spec, or\r\n    b) use spack uninstall -a to uninstall ALL matching specs.\r\n```\r\nafter the PR the two messages will be:\r\n```console\r\n$ spack find\r\n==> 0 installed packages.\r\n\r\n$ spack uninstall -a\r\n==> There are no package to uninstall.\r\n```",
